  "title": "AI GM - Campaign narrative (Loki, near-live)",
  "tags": ["ai-gm", "story", "loki", "narrative_turn", "memory_turn"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 9,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": { "from": "now-7d", "to": "now" },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "campaign_id",
        "label": "Campaign ID",
        "description": "Numer kampanii (np. 12). Zostaw .+ aby zobaczyć wszystkie.",
        "type": "textbox",
        "query": ".+",
        "current": { "value": ".+", "text": ".+" },
        "hide": 0,
        "skipUrlSync": false
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "datasource": null,
      "title": "Filtr",
      "gridPos": { "h": 2, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Wpisz ID kampanii w polu **Campaign ID** (np. `1033`). Zostaw `.+` żeby wyświetlić wszystkie.\n\n**Uwaga:** ten panel pokazuje tylko logi z **ostatnich 7 dni** (retencja Loki). Panel SQL może pokazywać starsze tury z bazy — jeśli tu jest pusto, sprawdź zakres czasu (prawy górny róg) albo czy po **streamingu** SSE doszło do `data: [DONE]` (bez tego tura nie zapisuje się i nie ma logu `narrative_turn`).\n\nPanel **Debug** niżej: surowe linie z `narrative_turn` bez parsowania `| json`."
      },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "Narrative turns — Gracz / GM",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 12, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 2 },
      "options": {
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "prettifyLogMessage": false,
        "showCommonLabels": false,
        "showLabels": false,
        "showTime": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending",
        "wrapLogMessage": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "{service=\"backend\"} |= \"narrative_turn\" | json | event=\"narrative_turn\" | campaign_id=~\"${campaign_id}\" | line_format \"[Kampania {{.campaign_id}} | Tura {{.turn_number}}]\\n\\nGRACZ:\\n{{.user_text}}\\n\\nGM:\\n{{.assistant_text}}\"",
          "queryType": "range",
          "legendFormat": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "Debug — surowe linie (bez | json)",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 14 },
      "options": {
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "prettifyLogMessage": false,
        "showCommonLabels": true,
        "showLabels": true,
        "showTime": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending",
        "wrapLogMessage": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "{service=\"backend\"} |= \"narrative_turn\"",
          "queryType": "range",
          "legendFormat": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "/mem turns — Pytanie / Odpowiedź",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 19 },
      "options": {
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
